In the INTEREST OF J.B. and J.B., Minor Children, J.B., Father, Appellant, A.T., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1807 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A father and a mother separately appeal the termination of their parental rights. REVERSED AND REMANDED ON BOTH APPEALS.

REVERSED AND REMANDED.
